title: Stardock Fences Pro 2.13 + KeyGen & Patch [GhostAgent47]
description:
Fences eliminates desktop clutter with adjustable fenced areas that organizes desktop objects into logical groups for quick access. Over 5 million users around the world rely on Fences every day to keep their PC desktops organized for quick and easy access to their programs and files they use most. The new Fences 2.14 features will now keep frequently used folders visible and organized on the desktop by creating a fence from any folder. Customization options direct Fences to automatically place new icons in designated fenced areas. Additionally, simple double click can hide or unhide all fence groups revealing an unobstructed view of the desktop.

Key Features:

- Create shaded areas to organize your desktop
- Double click the desktop to hide or show icons
- Define rules to organize your desktop icons
- Swipe between multiple pages of fences
- Create a different environment with different wallpapers across pages of fences
- Create a desktop portal from any folder

Instructions:

1. Unpack and install
2. Install first v 2.01 setup. Do not update to 2.13.
3. Copy Keymake and patch to installation directory
4. Patch and save licence
5. Make backup of the following SDActivate.exe sddlc.dll and sddlc64.dll
6. Now run setup 2.13 and copy and replace the backup files to installation directory. Do not update to 2.13.
7. Done
